E. Acquisition Strategy
The LG-N acquisition strategy is currently under development. The program office will look at ways to expand the industrial base, accelerate commercial preference,
develop incentives that maximize industry creativity, and create best value for the government while reducing program risk. With early and frequent engagement
between program office, operators, and industry, we will establish strong partnerships to take advantage of acquisition opportunities and balance acquisition and
operational risk. The LG-N Program Management Office (PMO) expects acquisition strategy approval in 4th quarter FY 2026.




