Description: Includes, but is not limited to, platform study, evaluation, and early experimentation activities to assess OFPs
against JSE Government Simulator Interface (GSI) and Simulator Common Architecture, Requirements, & Standards (SCARS),
and develop high-fidelity Platform OFP-based simulator and accompanying high-fidelity mission system and sensor models.
