Title: Transformational Technology Development                                                                                                0.000        0.000        1.438
Description: This effort is not a new start. In FY 2026, the Transformational Technology Development effort and associated
funding transferred within this Program Element from Project 633834, Integrated Space Technology Demonstrations to Project
630321, Space Warfighter Technologist Capabilities, to provide increased transparency and traceability of USSF S&T Vanguard
