upon, dominate conflicts in and from space. Advance technologies to enhance timeliness, performance, capacity, agility, and
resilience of US and allied space capabilities for transition to Program Executive Offices and to anchor future force designs.
Perform end-to-end space system technology development and experimentation from ground segment development to satellite
assembly, integration, and test to support multiple Department of the Air Force mission areas. Leverage first-of-a-kind space



