Continue execution of the NGJ-LB EMD contract focusing on pod (hardware and software) design, development
which will support system performance specification verification, subsystem qualification, and support interim
flight clearance for pod testing. Continue build of two (2) mission systems test pods and deliver (2) captive mass
models for aeromechanical flight test, which will reflect any design updates required from aeromechanical test
and analysis to assist with future mission systems pod testing. Continue development of PSE, provide data
to support EA-18G CIDD build and training materials in cooperation with the EA-18G aircraft OEM. Continue
Advanced Development of hardware and software to meet emerging threats that must be addressed within the
EMD phase.
FY 2027 Base Plans:
