award a contract modification (EMD Phase 2), capturing additional scope required to meet CDD threshold and
achieve Initial Operational Capability (IOC) by 3rd Quarter FY 2030. EMD Phase 2 includes the award of (6)
Systems Demonstration Test Articles (SDTA) NGJ-LB pods, accelerates the delivery of 8 Operational Prototype
Pods for an Early Operational Capability in 4Q FY 2029, supportability, logistics requirements and captures
additional Non-Recurring Engineering (NRE) to meet CDD threshold. FY 2027 includes delivery of two (2)

