D. Acquisition Strategy
The AN/ALQ-266 NGJ-LB program is designated an ACAT-IB Major Defense Acquisition Program (MDAP), MDAP program number 520. The activity will focus on the
Engineering and Manufacturing Development (EMD) phase, to develop and build (4) NGJ-LB test pods (2 aeromechanical and 2 mission systems), (8) Operational
Prototype Pods (OPP) for Early Operational Capability and (6) Systems Demonstration Test Articles (SDTA) to complete Initial Operational Test and Evaluation (IOT&E)
and achieve Initial Operational Capability (IOC).




