integration, and ground testing of the PTS-Prototype system in preparation for launch. Support Enhanced PTS-P technical design
reviews(delta PDR) and planned progress demonstrations to reduce integration risks. Distribute Testbed software and hardware
updates to industry and government users to support development and integration of PTW-enabled user terminal modems for
commercial constellations in both GEO and MEO orbits, aligning with Force Design objectives. Continue advancing PTW and the
PTW Testbed through ongoing development, testing, and exploration of new capabilities and features to keep pace with threat.
