testing, fielding, and early operations of Protected Tactical Waveform (PTW) over DoW and commercial constellations in GEO,
MEO, and HEO orbits and to ensure compatibility and interoperability among all segments. Continue to develop the PTW
Testbed's Key Management System (KMS) prototype to support of the development and integration of the operational PTW KMS
across all segments. Deploy, support, and maintain PTW Testbed instances across industry, government, and FFRDC facilities.
