Service (PTES) Mission planning and Key Management, namely the Mission Management System and Key Management
System (MMS/KMS) modifications. Integrates and updates program ground capability to plan and manage PTS-P/R, the
associated cryptographic material, and the SATCOM links enabling them to route and manage secure communication. Develops
and incorporates MMS modifications and capability with the WGS program ground segment for shared resource planning
and management (i.e., Common Network Planning Software (CNPS) and Wideband SATCOM Trend Analysis and Anomaly
Resolution System (WSTARS).

